(Vulois went to Cybertron for a few mintues, and now he's back. And 
Alloran, how can you know that the portal leads to Cybertron? I 
haven't told you yet.)

Vulois looks at Windrazor, and than at Child who is still trying to 
mkae it.

"Wait for Child to arrive, and than all will be revealed."


Brix and Fliq

Brix and Fliq finally pull themselves out from under the CR Chambers.

"Well, we've got them all up to 90% power. Now Fliq, if you want to 
do something, do it now. Soon we won't have time."

"I'm going to go for a little joy flight. How about you?"

"I'm gonna try to make peace with Bronco. We don't want him messing 
up our plans later."

"Alright. See you in a bit."

The two Maxis go there seperate ways.
